feedback_text: The app crashes every time I try to upload a file. This is blocking my work and urgent!
I love this product! It's made my workflow so much easier. Great job team!
Would be great if you could add dark mode feature. Many users have been requesting this.
The loading time is extremely slow. Takes forever to load the dashboard.
Your pricing is too expensive compared to competitors like Slack and Asana.
The interface is very confusing and hard to navigate. Too many clicks to do simple tasks.
Customer support team was very helpful and resolved my issue quickly. Thank you!
I'm concerned about data privacy. How is my information being encrypted and stored?
App is not working at all. Critical bug that needs immediate attention!
The new update is fantastic! Performance has improved significantly.
Missing integration with Google Calendar. This feature would be really useful.
UI design is cluttered and difficult to use. Needs better layout.
Your tool is much better than Trello. Switched last month and very happy.
Page freezes when I try to export reports. Happens every time.
Would love to see more customization options for the dashboard.
Support team never responds to my tickets. Been waiting for 3 days!
The free plan doesn't offer enough value. Need more features.
Worried about security vulnerabilities after recent data breaches in the news.
App is amazing! Makes collaboration so easy. Highly recommend.
Need a mobile app urgently. Only desktop version is limiting.
System hangs when processing large files. Very frustrating and slows down work.
Please add ability to export data in multiple formats like PDF and Excel.
Love the new dark theme! Looks professional and easy on the eyes.
Getting timeout errors frequently. Need this fixed ASAP.
The onboarding process was smooth and helpful. Great experience!
